headline: Peach State Health Plan and the Medical College of Georgia at Augusta University Celebrate 2025 Peach State Scholars
summary: Peach State Health Plan, a leading care management organization serving Georgia and a Centene Corporation subsidiary, and the Medical College of Georgia at Augusta University (MCG) proudly recognized the newest cohort of Peach State Scholars during a special pinning ceremony.

headline: Will the Centene (CNC) Lawsuit Shift Investor Perceptions of Management Credibility and Disclosure?
summary: In August 2025, Bleichmar Fonti & Auld LLP announced that a lawsuit was filed against Centene Corporation and certain executives alleging violations of federal securities laws, following the company's abrupt withdrawal of prior financial guidance in July after an independent report revealed lower-than-expected market growth and higher morbidity in key states.
